column4: EU court seen ruling on Intel antitrust case next year - judge
column5: PARIS  June 26 Europe's top court is likely to rule on Intel's appeal against a record 1.06 billion euro ($1.19 billion) EU antitrust fine next year  an EU judge said on Monday  a case that may affect companies such as Google and Qualcomm in the EU's crosshairs.
